{
  "texts": [
    "We have therefore used our own approximation of Clarivate's method based on Scopus data to estimate the effect.",
    "All other factors being equal, we have only altered the selection of highly-cited papers, excluding papers with 30 or more authors versus 30 or more affiliations.",
    "For the period 2010-2018, the number of HCRs in Germany increases by 2.1% from 1,543 to 1,576 authors.",
    "For Switzerland, the number decreases by 8.5% from 800 HCRs based on the exclusion of papers with 30 or more affiliations to 732 HCRs (when papers with 30 or more authors were excluded).",
    "Smaller countries show even larger relative effects than larger countries."
  ]
}